M.M. CHAWLA V. J.S. SETHI [1969] INSC 243 (15 September 1969)

 15/09/1969 
ACT:
 Delhi Rent Control Act 1958--Suit for ejectment for non- payment of rent for three consecutive months--Tenant in written statement claiming fixation of standard rent--Such claim made after period of limitation laid dawn in s. 12 cannot be entertained--Ss. 4, 5, 6 or 15(3) do not support claim--Benefit under s. 14(2) for a second time barred by proviso to sub-section.
 
